On the desktop client on VRChat, users with [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] are able to utilize [[Special:MyLanguage/Selfie Expression|Selfie Expression]] with a webcam, to enable a limited variant of hand and finger tracking on their avatar. Selfie Expression uses your camera to animate your avatar! No one will see your real face. Image data is processed locally on your device, only used for animation, and never saved.